    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Benchmark Your Skills</strong> is an interactive platform that offers a wide variety of tests and games designed to measure and improve cognitive abilities. With tools that assess memory, reaction time, reflexes, and mental processing capabilities, the platform is perfect for anyone looking to challenge their brain and enhance their performance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main tests include the <strong>Reaction Time</strong>, which measures your response speed to visual stimuli, and <strong>Sequence</strong>, which challenges your ability to remember complex sequences. Additionally, <strong>Benchmark Your Skills</strong> records your scores, allowing you to compare your results with users from around the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194810/extras/9382da26f7904e216419a167c5ab38e7.poster.avif?t=1737258733\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194810/extras/9382da26f7904e216419a167c5ab38e7.webm?t=1737258733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194810/extras/9382da26f7904e216419a167c5ab38e7.mp4?t=1737258733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194810/extras/d5e5f5d84e4650d77a60e5e08f81e996.poster.avif?t=1737258733\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194810/extras/d5e5f5d84e4650d77a60e5e08f81e996.webm?t=1737258733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194810/extras/d5e5f5d84e4650d77a60e5e08f81e996.mp